# Private plugins (e.g. a closed-source overlay) are symlinked into this folder
# at dev/build time and must NEVER be committed to this public repository.
# Ignore everything here except the public plugins explicitly allowlisted below.
#
# Keep generic plugin SPI code OUT of this folder (it lives under src/store or
# src/lib) so the allowlist can stay folder-only.
/*
!.gitignore
!comet/
!development/
